  "keyFeatures": [
    "Stream blockchain data from Subsquid Portal datasets for EVM, Solana, and Hyperliquid chains",
    "Strongly-typed event decoders with ABI support for EVM contracts",
    "Factory contract pattern support for dynamic contract tracking",
    "Built-in targets for ClickHouse and PostgreSQL with Drizzle ORM",
    "Fork-aware processing with automatic rollback handling",
    "Composable pipeline architecture via pipe() helper",
    "Profiling, structured logging, and Prometheus metrics",
    "Portal caching for improved performance"
  ],
